To Make the Sliders: Preheat oven 450Â°F. Line baking sheet with foil. In large bowl, combine all ingredients except rolls using 4 tablespoons hoisin sauce. Form into miniature patties (heaping tablespoons depending on size of bun) and place on prepared pan. Brush tops of burgers with remaining 2 tablespoons hoisin sauce. Bake 10-12 minutes or until done. Slit rolls and place burger with about a tablespoon Pineapple Salsa. To Make the Salsa: In bowl, mix together all ingredients. Refrigerate.